<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KHAMHNAK HLA CH460</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A kan Khamhtu a kan dawtnak, Khua-ruahhar nak ngaingai a si ko, Van in
 leiah a rung tum kha, Kannih kha a kan dawt ca a si, a si, Kannih kha a
 kan dawt ca a si.

[C1]
   A si, a si, kan caah A si ko, kan ca, Kan Bawi a rung tum i
   zaang-fahnak um lo-in Vailam-tahnak cungah an thah.

[V2]
 A thi chuahnak le a innak, Thihnak vialte a fak bik a in, Khuazei tal
 ah an chim cang maw, Sifah le retheih a huahnak kha, nak kha, Sifah le
 retheih a huahnak kha.

[C2]
   A si, a si, kan caah A si ko, kan ca, Kan Bawi a rung tum i
   zaang-fahnak um lo-in Vailam-tahnak cungah an thah.

[V3]
 Khi khua tha bik kong ka theih cang, Bawi Khrih a zummi nih an co lai,
 Sihmanhseh van khuathar ah khin, Kei umnak tah a remh cang hnga maw, hnga
 maw? Kei umnak tah a remh cang hnga maw?

[C3]
   A si, a si, kan caah A si ko, kan ca, Kan Bawi a rung tum i
   zaang-fahnak um lo-in Vailam-tahnak cungah an thah.

[V4]
 Bawipa kan halnak run ka ngai, Nangmah hlei in a tha hodah um? Na
 Thiang Thlarau in run ka chim, Van inntha le ka Khamhtu Bawi kong, Bawi
 kong, Van inntha le ka Khamhtu Bawi kong.

[C4]
   A si, a si, kan caah A si ko, kan ca, Kan Bawi a rung tum i
   zaang-fahnak um lo-in Vailam-tahnak cungah an thah.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<hymn_number>460</hymn_number>
</song>